nodes.text: The F1-XD Autorepair Droid was a type of repair probe droid used as security forces by the Selkath species on the planet Manaan during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. A number of them were part of the security forces of Genetics Laboratory G-1.

The F1-XD Autorepair Droid appears a type of enemy in the Tactical Flashpoint "Depths of Manaan," which was first added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic: Rise of the Hutt Cartel in Game Update 2.9: Galactic Strongholds Early Access. Similarly to the AD-4 Battledroid Centurion, the F1-XD is given a generic name in the Solo Mode version of the Flashpoint rather than the designation used in the full version.
